8-OtWif8Z4A.title: 10 Years Of NCS
8-OtWif8Z4A.description:
10 years ago today, NoCopyrightSounds was born. I sat down at my computer, opened YouTube & created this channel. I wanted to create a community for creators to find copyright safe music, but it became so much more than that… it became a family of creators, artists & fans. 

We would not be where we are today without the support of the artists, the content creators and of course YOU, the fans. Thank you for the past 10 years, and we’re incredibly excited for what the future brings!

Over the next few months we’ll be celebrating by releasing some epic new music every week from some of your favourite artists.
Sign up here to get the NCS10 releases before anyone else - https://ncs.io/10 

Don’t forget to get involved on our socials to take part in all things NCS10!
